  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.3,
      "size": 20880,
      "text": "定积分能求出曲线下方的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "那么一张起伏的曲面下方，又该怎样求出它包住的体积呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.24,
      "size": 19872,
      "text": "这正是二重积分要回答的问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "在矩形区域上，我们把曲面下方的立体切成许许多多细长的小柱子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "每根柱子的体积，等于底面小块的面积乘以那里的函数高度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "把所有柱子的体积加起来，就得到二重积分，写作对 f 关于面积元 dA 的积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "itr-1",
      "filename": "iterate-itr-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/iterate-itr-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "实际计算时，我们把它拆成两次一维积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "itr-2",
      "filename": "iterate-itr-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/iterate-itr-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "先固定 y，沿 x 方向积一刀，得到一个截面的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "itr-3",
      "filename": "iterate-itr-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/iterate-itr-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "再让这个面积沿 y 方向累加起来，体积就求出来了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "approx",
      "line_id": "apx-1",
      "filename": "approx-apx-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/approx-apx-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "在屏幕上，我们把区域划成 n 乘 n 的网格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "approx",
      "line_id": "apx-2",
      "filename": "approx-apx-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/approx-apx-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "取每个小格的中心点算出高度，颜色越暖表示柱子越高。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "approx",
      "line_id": "apx-3",
      "filename": "approx-apx-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/approx-apx-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "把每根柱子的体积相加，就是逼近真实体积的黎曼和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "试着调大网格密度，看近似的体积如何一步步逼近真值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "再换不同的函数和区域，观察热力图和体积怎样随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "二重积分把曲面下方的体积，化成无数小柱子的累加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "累次积分让我们先横后纵地一步步算出它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "multiple-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/multiple-integral/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "网格越密，逼近越准，这就是重积分的思想，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
